Spring Boot

To start / get a baseline for creating an API, go to Spring Initializr

Spring Initializr > enter details and dependencies and download basic source code.
Dependencies like Spring Web, Spring boot Dev tools.

Spring web is used to create web based APIs.

Download the file, extract and open it.

pom.xml file contains all the dependencies required for API creation. We can add / remove dependencies based on requirement.

@SpringBootApplication is the entry point.

